.:: Puzzle 6x7-Level-2-1::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: coffee, iced-tea, almond-milk, hot-chocolate, cola, sprite, 7up
The people have 7 different hobbies: magic-tricks, writing, dancing, skydiving, gardening, hiking, puzzles
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: epic, martial-arts, family, western, drama, thriller, zombie
There are 7 different nationalities: thai, nigerian, indian, chinese, japanese, colombian, russian
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: swimming, weightlifting, water-polo, sailing, snowboarding, handball, biathlon
The people use 7 different means of transport: helicopter, car, jet-ski, trike, snowmobile, bike, boat
 1. the person watching zombie movies is the person driving the bike##1
 2. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the left of the chinese##1
 3. the person driving the helicopter is on the far left##1
 4. the person who's sport is swimming is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
 5. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
 6. the chinese is on the left of the person driving the car##1
 7. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
 8. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is the person driving the car##1
 9. the person watching zombie movies is the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
10. the person who's hobby is writing is the nigerian##1
11. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the left of the person watching western movies##1
12. the person who's sport is swimming is the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
13. the person drinking almond-milk is between the person who's sport is sailing and the person who's sport is weightlifting##2
14. the japanese is on the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
15. the person drinking 7up is the person watching thriller movies##1
16. the nigerian is on the far right##1
17. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the left of the nigerian##1
18. the person driving the helicopter is the person who's hobby is gardening##1
19. the person who's hobby is writing is on the right of the person driving the trike##1
20. the person driving the jet-ski is on the right of the person watching western movies##1
21. the indian is on the right of the japanese##1
22. the person watching family movies is on the far right##1
23. the japanese is in the middle##1
24. the colombian is the person drinking iced-tea##1
25. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
26. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the person who's sport is handball##1
27. the person watching epic movies is the russian##1
28. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the right of the person driving the jet-ski##1
29. the person watching epic movies is on the left of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
